semkit.extractor

Class WikiMetaXMLDecoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • semkit.extractor.WikiMetaXMLDecoder

  • public class WikiMetaXMLDecoder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class builds an object that represents an annotated document retrieved from Wikimeta API under an XML form.

    Note that this class allows to retrieve more that 3 candidates as the public version of the Wikimeta API does. This has been introduced for the NIST KBP2013 campaign where the specific Wikimeta Server used can return 15 candidates.
    Author:
    ericcharton
